# 💫 About Me:

I am a passionate Mechanical Engineer with a strong interest in design, manufacturing, and industrial engineering solutions.<br><br>Currently learning advanced mechanical design concepts, product development, and modern manufacturing technologies to gain practical industry experience.<br><br>Skilled in CAD modeling, mechanical drafting, product design, and engineering analysis, with hands-on experience in software like AutoCAD, SolidWorks, CATIA, Creo, and ANSYS.<br><br>I enjoy designing efficient mechanical systems, creating innovative engineering solutions, and working on real-world industrial projects.<br><br>Continuously exploring new technologies and developing practical projects to strengthen my technical and problem-solving skills.

